# BINA SIMULATION v3.01alpha

It isn't main branch. App provides 3-body breakup simulation with (SSA) (others rections in previous version 2.11)

## INSTALLATION

### building program

- `mkdir build && cd build`
- `cmake -DGeant4_Dir=<path to geant4 install dir> ../`
- `make -j<threads>`

## RUN

- `root .l pluto.mac (need to set pluto_path) `
- `./pluto_convert`
- `./bina_run`

or

- `./auto`

## Params

Main parameters can be found in geo.mac
